  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Retro Shooter Experience: Relive the nostalgia of classic boomer shooters with fast-paced, heart-racing gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/1f589b5d0759811271b4666dde6827f8.poster.avif?t=1765193292\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/1f589b5d0759811271b4666dde6827f8.webm?t=1765193292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/1f589b5d0759811271b4666dde6827f8.mp4?t=1765193292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Upgrades: Complete additional quests in each level to earn minor upgrades for your arsenal, enhancing your firepower and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Rooms and Secret Weapons: Explore every nook and cranny to discover hidden rooms and unlock powerful secret weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse Enemies and Levels: Battle through a variety of levels filled with numerous enemies, each with unique abilities and challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/fd8d862eef95572cb61677fe9482427e.poster.avif?t=1765193292\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/fd8d862eef95572cb61677fe9482427e.webm?t=1765193292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/fd8d862eef95572cb61677fe9482427e.mp4?t=1765193292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Boss Fights: Test your skills against several formidable bosses, each requiring different tactics and strategies to defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Epic Final Showdown: Face the ultimate challenge as you confront Satan in an epic final boss battle.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic Retro Shooter Experience: Relive the nostalgia of classic boomer shooters with fast-paced, heart-racing gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/1f589b5d0759811271b4666dde6827f8.poster.avif?t=1765193292\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/1f589b5d0759811271b4666dde6827f8.webm?t=1765193292\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/1f589b5d0759811271b4666dde6827f8.mp4?t=1765193292\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Weapon Upgrades: Complete additional quests in each level to earn minor upgrades for your arsenal, enhancing your firepower and strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Rooms and Secret Weapons: Explore every nook and cranny to discover hidden rooms and unlock powerful secret weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Diverse Enemies and Levels: Battle through a variety of levels filled with numerous enemies, each with unique abilities and challenges.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/fd8d862eef95572cb61677fe9482427e.poster.avif?t=1765193292\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2997260/extras/fd8d862eef95572cb61677fe9482427e.webm?t=1765193292\" type=\"video/we